data.text:
Picture Window Pro

Picture Window Pro is an image editing tool with a comprehensive set of photo manipulation and retouching tools that allow you to control and shape every aspect of your images.

Chasys Draw IES

Chasys Draw IES is a suite of image editing applications, including a layer-based image editor with adjustment layers, linked layers, timeline and frame-based animation, icon editing, image stacking, and comprehensive plug-in support.

PhotoFiltre

PhotoFiltre is an image editing and effects program with standard adjustment functions (brightness, contrast, dyed, saturation, gamma correction) and also artistic filters (watercolor, pastels, Indian ink, pointillism, puzzle effect).

Pinta

Pinta is an open-source, cross-platform bitmap image drawing and editing program modeled after Paint.NET, a similar image editing program limited to Windows.

Paint.NET

Paint.NET is an image editing software for Windows that features an intuitive and innovative user interface with support for layers, unlimited undo, special effects, and a wide variety of useful tools.

PhotoFilters

PhotoFilters is a simple online tool that lets you apply many different filters and effects to your photos and images.

PhotoEnlarger

PhotoEnlarger is an online tool that helps you enlarge your photos and uses filters to make them less pixelated. You can select from four different enlargements results the tool generates.

BeFunky

BeFunky is a powerful yet easy-to-use photo editor, collage maker, and graphic design tool.
